<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Telecom Company Email Template</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    a {
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Telecom Company</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <p>Dear [Customer Name],</p>
<#if condition>true<#else>false</#if>
    <p>This is a sample email from Telecom Company. You can use this template to create your own email campaigns. Be sure to customize the content to match your specific needs.</p>

    <p>Here are some tips for creating effective email campaigns:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Use a clear and concise subject line.</li>
      <li>Personalize your emails whenever possible.</li>
      <li>Keep your emails brief and to the point.</
      <li>Use a call to action to tell your recipients what you want them to do next.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Thank you for your business!</p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>

    <p>The Telecom Company Team</p>

    <footer>
      <a href="#">Visit our website</a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
